_sText: The purpose of this remake was essencially to make the map look better, I used to play this map a lot in a few public servers for long time. So I've been thinking about making a remake of it, and here it is. beta 1_________________ Improvements: + 3dskybox + Detail + texture work improved + env_sun + light_env _______________________ I dont know the author of the original map, I searched for the map here on the banana to see if I could find the author but I didnt. Anyway I prefer to leave all the credits of the map to him and to valve. Have fun!
